  "text": "Mimics and inhibitors for hsa-miR-675-5p (as well as respective negative control siRNAs) were purchased from RiboBio (Guangzhou, China). AsPC-1 and PANC-1 cells were transfected with either 50 nM hsa-miR-675-5p mimic or 100 nM hsa-miR-675-5p inhibitor according to the manufacturer's protocol. Either a mixture of three siRNAs targeting H19 (siH19) or negative control siRNAs (NC) were used as previously described [CITATION_1] . Lipofectamine 2000 was adopted as a transfection reagent, and the transfection efficiency was confirmed using qPCR.",
